{"tid":53101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好容易陷入幻想？","createTime":"2016-12-24T12:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T16:21:43.000Z","uid":17696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7185fee642ae2ad76799dd67139d101c1ed46ce","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"會成日不停諗野無論係現實或者係不真實<br />\n經常失神 要畀人叫幾次先回到魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得好耐之前睇完套小說之後<br />\n不停幻想一個世界 之後又有睇權力遊戲<br />\n開始不斷地架構一個世界 又因為想真實啲<br />\n成日上wiki 又不停睇啲風俗服裝書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲資料我到宜家仲keep緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都係因為咁我愛上左歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a3251f8b77e39a274ec2868ce40ec7b0a797d0","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"5c49fe30adaf23e68ab05fcfc9d5b47b16a85efc","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"病"},{"pid":"90069166ff0e02c0975ecd73aa888500aebbe9d4","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"就"},{"pid":"17d770fc2f5a5a06aa04cbe9059d558ebb230c90","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"該"},{"pid":"3ab21838d3b054306a79dea9580a33feef34fe43","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"吃"},{"pid":"bc84d025da51dd6f2ab7ce72ef52f0056e3f6abd","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"藥"},{"pid":"3af7bcf32d4c824ec0f04b8f9d8252f496a19dbd","tid":53101,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,