wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8eadd84d326eeadd8944eca91aac9b0c1dbccf","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n<br />\n之前成日上膠登寫未來日記同自貼<br />\n<br />\n幻想操控世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係齋諗唔會同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56309e323e696ca1a08f4c0203bb58f613d1f686","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"有時會不斷同自己辯論 諗同人講野要講咩會最適合 最有回響<br />\n<br />\n我是咪好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804605f34f6e741c0a7bff2e4b4b0cc09e132570","tid":53101,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪都係山羊座??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2ab43212eac4f052464bbdc769e574fdfb6b5e","tid":53101,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣不過我樂在其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345823916782b5a57288ba7d04a0e9b63566f3b6","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係咪都係山羊座??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雙魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打可以睇少啲星座啦"},{"pid":"ec47ef45e35add56e54886f85973b959e035e798","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣不過我樂在其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都樂在其中呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bce17341db9d90af7a39f6ed3c665a5085053f","tid":53101,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樓主一樣不過我樂在其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都樂在其中呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇書有畫面真係好正既享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26be719be94bf717906a596b7c9493d2ab2db53e","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同樓主一樣不過我樂在其中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都樂在其中呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇書有畫面真係好正既享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過我會睇得好慢 因為睇睇下又會好自然陷入左幻想到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d7f7fa883870c548427de1daf8564411d34e27","tid":53101,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"樓主中左月讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c535db3bb2243b9c6389817d9c57faad9942e0b7","tid":53101,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"唔是幻想是中了幻術"},{"pid":"646686afa7bef6e6e68a793cb7a51e18505b8054","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主中左月讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b8ecbb82a356f6d9e95f562b5ace51f813a92c","tid":53101,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"精神病既一種強迫思考症"},{"pid":"27cba8bc52b76acebf68bcd970e6ed77e6eb694b","tid":53101,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aaf2ae2a51d0ffc0657ce0e5e524e66dde7121","tid":53101,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n分唔清幾時係現實幾時係幻想<br />\n有時覺得現實好唔真實"},{"pid":"6a7403297e90538a0cd86f2521dd2693c43412f9","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神病既一種強迫思考症</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓 得唔得講多少少"},{"pid":"779f9b5097c7b8270058a901e1fc7279b02c5706","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n分唔清幾時係現實幾時係幻想<br />\n有時覺得現實好唔真實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未止於咁 不過巴打好似陷得太深啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131dd63efbbcc3cfd098e514419da034ced05607","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b158df013e26083fde8ef82c6146724e11ab280f","tid":53101,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時會不斷同自己辯論 諗同人講野要講咩會最適合 最有回響<br />\n<br />\n我是咪好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪諗到好多野，但係一比人駁就口啞啞<br />\n過一陣又會諗到點駁佢，之後就會覺得自己果陣好柒<br />\n<br />\nbtw你呢啲叫發緊夢"},{"pid":"e4f7d57d52f7aad9436e5b52b4a44fdaaa7d8217","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時會不斷同自己辯論 諗同人講野要講咩會最適合 最有回響<br />\n<br />\n我是咪好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪諗到好多野，但係一比人駁就口啞啞<br />\n過一陣又會諗到點駁佢，之後就會覺得自己果陣好柒<br />\n<br />\nbtw你呢啲叫發緊夢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我自己有少少鬱躁症傾向 一開著個制真係幾嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係平時會不停諗同人講咩 雖然最後都唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07459cff8541b141cc3f26e3f22bc1ac49cb909f","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4daff937f607d8941621d9e0934c32f1b1e9db34","tid":53101,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67a5d67300ebe7eb806db5a964a36ebb0454a0b","tid":53101,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過將你嘅世界寫成小說同人分享"},{"pid":"beca0bf93e7798521739e8be0c05298827fc72fa","tid":53101,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇自己作故 ????"}]}